# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Refactoring Factory — Worksheet Examiner
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Copy to .env and fill in values.

# ── Anthropic [REQUIRED] ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by: Worksheet Examiner (/api/assess)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ── Cartesia Voice AI [OPTIONAL] ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Without this, TTS falls back to browser speechSynthesis
# and STT falls back to Web Speech API.
CARTESIA_API_KEY=

# Examiner voice — Cartesia voice ID
# Default: British female. Browse: https://play.cartesia.ai/voices
CARTESIA_EXAMINER_VOICE_ID=79a125e8-cd45-4c13-8a67-188112f4dd22

# TTS model
CARTESIA_MODEL=sonic-2
